m now weighing the immediate need for Firebase setup against the option of local storage. The instructions highlight the risk of lost user data from cleared browser caches, and the project is meant to log student interaction. I\'m leaning toward initiating Firebase setup now, considering its mandate and the potential for significant data loss if I delay. I\'ll need to figure out a suitable way to indicate to the user that they must allow Firebase setup before continuing.\n\n\n"
