  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Natural Tones\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Natural Tones\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#f8f7f2] flex flex-col font-sans text-[#2d2d2d] overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <nav class=\\\"h-16 border-b border-[#e5e1d5] flex items-center justify-between px-8 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-[#5a5a40] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-4 h-4 bg-white rounded-sm rotate-45\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n      <span class=\\\"font-serif italic text-xl font-bold text-[#5a5a40]\\\">Voice2Literacy</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex gap-2 bg-[#efede4] p-1 rounded-full\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white text-sm font-medium shadow-sm\\\">Student Lab</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-[#7d796b]\\\">Teacher Dashboard</button>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#5a5a40] p-0.5\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-full h-full rounded-full bg-[#d9d5c5] flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold\\\">AM</div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <section class=\\\"flex-[1.8] p-8 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-1\\\">\\n          <h1 class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif font-medium\\\">Hi, Alex! \360\237\221\213</h1>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[#7d796b]\\\">What\'s your story idea for today?</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#fff9ed] border border-[#f5e1bc] px-4 py-2 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#9d7d2d]\\\">Current Focus</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"font-serif italic text-[#5a5a40]\\\">The Stop Sign (Punctuation)</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-white rounded-[32px] border border-[#e5e1d5] shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute top-6 left-8 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#e65a5a] animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter text-[#7d796b]\\\">Listening for your voice...</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"w-full max-w-2xl text-center space-y-8\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#fcfaf7] border-2 border-dashed border-[#d9d5c5] rounded-2xl p-6\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-[#9a9582] uppercase mb-3 tracking-widest\\\">\360\237\223\235 Your Spoken Idea</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-serif text-[#5a5a40] leading-relaxed italic\\\">\\n              \\\"the dragon flew over the mountain and he saw a big castle and then he breathed fire on the grass\\\"\\n            </p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center gap-6\\\">\\n            <button class=\\\"w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-[#5a5a40] shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center ring-8 ring-[#5a5a40]/10\\\">\\n              <svg class=\\\"w-10 h-10 text-white\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-20a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 006 0V5a3 3 0 00-3-3z\\\"></path></svg>\\n            </button>\\n            <div class=\\\"bg-[#f5f9f2] text-[#4a5a40] px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border border-[#d5e5cc] text-center max-w-lg\\\">\\n              <p class=\\\"font-medium\\\">Great imagination! \360\237\220\211 I see a few long sentences. Can you find where a <span class=\\\"underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4\\\">Stop Sign</span> (period) should go?</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n    <aside class=\\\"flex-1 bg-[#f1f0e8] border-l border-[#e5e1d5] p-8 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#7d796b]\\\">Class Insights</h2>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-[#d9d5c5] uppercase\\\">Live View</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-[#e5e1d5]\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-[#9a9582] mb-1\\\">Engagement</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-end gap-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif leading-none\\\">4.8</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#829a84] font-bold pb-1\\\">/ 5.0</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-[#e5e1d5]\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-[#9a9582] mb-1\\\">Confidence</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-end gap-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-3xl font-serif leading-none\\\">92%</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-[#829a84] font-bold pb-1\\\">\342\206\221 4%</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-[#e5e1d5] flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-serif text-lg mb-4 italic\\\">Mastery Breakdown</h3>\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-4 flex-1\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-xs font-bold\\\">\\n              <span>Punctuation (P)</span>\\n              <span>65%</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"h-2 bg-[#f0f0ea] rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"h-full bg-[#5a5a40] w-[65%]\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-xs font-bold\\\">\\n              <span>Capitalization (C)</span>\\n              <span>88%</span>\